        <characteristic name="Special Rules" typeId="5f83-3633-336b-93b4">Armour Bane (1), Bombardment, Cumbersome, Move or Shoot, Multiple Wounds (D3)</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="Notes" typeId="772a-a7ff-f6b3-df71">This weapon does not use its crews Ballistic Skill. Instead, it shoots like a stone thrower, using the Bombardment special rule. This weapon uses a 5&quot; blast template and the Black Powder Misfire table. The Multiple Wounds (D3) special rule applies only to a single model whose base lies underneath the central hole of the blast template.</characteristic>
